{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Raise the Tax-Free Personal Allowance to \u00a316,000 in the next tax year",
        "additional_details": "By increasing the standard Personal Allowance from \u00a312,570 to \u00a316,000 we can support average UK workers.\r\n \r\nWe ended December 2023 with an inflation rate of 4.0%. This economic climate has left many struggling to make ends meet, with some full time workers having to use food banks.\r\n",
        "background": "The current standard Personal Allowance is \u00a312,570. However, with the current economic challenges and increased living costs, we believe the \u00a312,570 allowance is no longer sufficient for many people.",
